---

<section id="about">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title">About</h2>
    <div class="about-content">
      <p>
        I'm a PhD candidate in Physics at <strong>Northeastern University</strong>, affiliated with the
        <a href="https://www.mighte.org/" target="_blank">MIGHTE Lab</a>
        (PI: Mauricio Santillana). My research sits at the intersection of machine learning
        and data science with epidemiology and health care.
      </p>
      <p>
        I build ML systems and data-driven solutions that have real-world impact: an early warning
        system for respiratory disease across all 50 US states, built in collaboration with the
        <strong>CDC</strong>; a deep learning pipeline to detect diabetic retinopathy from
        retinal images; and Bayesian/MCMC frameworks for uncertainty quantification in
        outbreak forecasting models. My day-to-day involves working with large-scale,
        messy datasets, from data ingestion and analysis through modeling, experimentation,
        and communicating results to both technical and non-technical stakeholders.
      </p>
      <p>
        I'm actively seeking roles in <strong>data science</strong>, <strong>machine learning</strong>,
        and <strong>applied science</strong> where I can bring research-level rigor and
        end-to-end pipeline experience to production systems.
      </p>

      <div class="tabs-section">
        <div class="tab-buttons">
          <button class="tab-btn active" data-tab="education">Education</button>
          <button class="tab-btn" data-tab="experience">Experience</button>
        </div>

        <div class="tab-content active" id="education">
          <div class="edu-item">
            <span class="edu-degree">Ph.D. in Physics (expected)</span>
            <span class="edu-detail">Northeastern University, Boston MA, May 2027</span>
          </div>
          <div class="edu-item">
            <span class="edu-degree">M.Sc. in Physics</span>
            <span class="edu-detail">Northeastern University, Boston MA, May 2024</span>
          </div>
          <div class="edu-item">
            <span class="edu-degree">B.S. in Physics</span>
            <span class="edu-detail">Purdue University Northwest, IN, May 2022</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tab-content" id="experience">
          <div class="exp-item">
            <div class="exp-header">
              <span class="exp-role">Research Assistant</span>
              <span class="exp-duration">05/2023 – Present</span>
            </div>
            <span class="exp-company">Northeastern University, Boston, MA</span>
          </div>
          <div class="exp-item">
            <div class="exp-header">
              <span class="exp-role">Research Assistant</span>
              <span class="exp-duration">06/2021 – 09/2021</span>
            </div>
            <span class="exp-company">University of California Davis, Davis, CA</span>
          </div>
          <div class="exp-item">
            <div class="exp-header">
              <span class="exp-role">Teaching Assistant</span>
              <span class="exp-duration">09/2022 – 12/2023</span>
            </div>
            <span class="exp-company">Northeastern University, Boston, MA</span>
          </div>
          <div class="exp-item">
            <div class="exp-header">
              <span class="exp-role">Private Tutor</span>
              <span class="exp-duration">08/2021 – 05/2022</span>
            </div>
            <span class="exp-company">Purdue University Northwest, IN</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-content p {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    max-width: 720px;
  }

  .about-content p:last-of-type {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .tabs-section {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    max-width: 720px;
  }

  .tab-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .tab-btn {
    padding: 0.6rem 1.5rem;
    background: none;
    border: none;
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    cursor: pointer;
    position: relative;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .tab-btn::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -2px;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 2px;
    background: transparent;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }

  .tab-btn:hover {
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .tab-btn.active {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .tab-btn.active::after {
    background: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .tab-content {
    display: none;
  }

  .tab-content.active {
    display: block;
  }

  .edu-item {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    padding: 0.75rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .edu-item:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .edu-degree {
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .edu-detail {
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .exp-item {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    padding: 0.75rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .exp-item:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .exp-header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .exp-role {
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .exp-duration {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .exp-company {
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }
</style>

<script>
  document.querySelectorAll('.tab-btn').forEach(btn => {
    btn.addEventListener('click', () => {
      const tab = btn.dataset.tab;

      document.querySelectorAll('.tab-btn').forEach(b => b.classList.remove('active'));
      document.querySelectorAll('.tab-content').forEach(c => c.classList.remove('active'));

      btn.classList.add('active');
      document.getElementById(tab)?.classList.add('active');
    });
  });
</script>
